OL,3,CWest Coast Mainline rail disruption:
OL,4,Cwhat you need to know
OL,6,FThere will be continued Easter
OL,7,Fdisruption on the West Coast Main Line
OL,8,Fthis weekend to allow for the biggest
OL,9,Foverhaul of the railway in more than
OL,10,F50 years, with #400m upgrades from
OL,11,FEuston in the South to Preston in the
OL,12,FNorth.
OL,14,FPassengers are urged to check before
OL,15,Fthey travel as no trains will be
OL,16,Frunning between Preston and Lancaster
OL,17,Ffrom April 11-20.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/7
