OL,3,CWest Coast Mainline rail disruption:
OL,4,Cwhat you need to know
OL,6,FTrains will divert onto the Settle-
OL,7,FCarlisle line and trains will run
OL,8,Fbetween Oxenholme and Carlisle. Bus
OL,9,Freplacement services will also be in
OL,10,Fplace.
OL,12,FIt follows similar disruption during
OL,13,Fthe Easter bank holiday weekend when
OL,14,Fthere were no trains between Preston
OL,15,Fand Oxenholme, which also saw
OL,16,Fdiversions onto the Settle-Carlisle
OL,17,Fline and bus replacement services.
OL,19,FThe Settle-Carlisle diversion
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
