OL,3,CWest Coast Mainline rail disruption:
OL,4,Cwhat you need to know
OL,6,FThe picturesque Settle-Carlisle line
OL,7,Fwill be opened to passengers from
OL,8,FApril 11-20. Passengers can board at
OL,9,FCarlisle to travel to Preston, or vice-
OL,10,Fversa.
OL,12,FPassengers travelling between
OL,13,FOxenholme and Carlisle can still
OL,14,Ftravel by train, with bus replacements
OL,15,Fto the north and south.
OL,17,FChanges on Saturday April 11
OL,19,FChanges on Saturday April 12
OL,21,FChanges April 13 ` 18
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/7
