OL,3,CWest Coast Mainline rail disruption:
OL,4,Cwhat you need to know
OL,6,FChanges on Sunday April 19
OL,8,FWhat's causing the disruption?
OL,10,FThe West Coast Mainline is Europe's
OL,11,Fbusiest mixed-use railway, carrying
OL,12,Falmost 2,000 passenger trains and
OL,13,F15,000 tonnes of goods every day.
OL,14,FPassenger numbers are expected to
OL,15,Fdouble by 2050.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/7
