OL,3,CWest Coast Mainline rail disruption:
OL,4,Cwhat you need to know
OL,6,FJulien Dehornoy, North West & Central
OL,7,FDeputy Regional Managing Director at
OL,8,FNetwork Rail, said: "The West Coast
OL,9,FMain Line is one of Britain's most
OL,10,Fimportant railway lines. We're
OL,11,Finvesting in it over this Easter
OL,12,Fperiod to ensure a more reliable,
OL,13,Fresilient railway that communities and
OL,14,Fbusinesses can depend on for decades
OL,15,Fto come.
OL,17,F"Passengers should be aware that this
OL,18,Fwork will mean some changes to
OL,19,Fjourneys and should plan their trips
OL,20,Fahead of time."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/7
